* B. Search Agents
** ndtut                        Lookup tutorial program.
** ndic                         Using free dictionaries.
** ndeb                         Using CD-ROM dictionaries.
** ndtp                         Using NDTP dictionary server.
** ndict                        Using DICT dictionary server.
** ndsrd                        Using Random House Dictionary.
** ndnmz                        Using Namazu for text search.
** ndkks                        Using KAKASI for Japanese words.
** ndspell                      Using Ispell to check and search words.
** ndcookie                     Using cookie file for fun.

* C. Dictionary Types
** SDIC                         The SDIC format.
** dictd                        The format used by dictd.
** cookie                       The cookie file format.
** EB/EPWING                    The EB/EBG/EBXA/EPWING format.
** NDTP                         The Network Dictionary Transport Protocol.
** DICT                         The DICT internet dictionary protocol.

